&lt;p&gt;English | &lt;a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lruihao/caniuse-embed-element/refs/heads/main./README.zh-cn.md" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;简体中文&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A lightweight, customizable web component that embeds &lt;a href="https://caniuse.com" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;caniuse.com&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; browser compatibility data for specific web features. Built with &lt;a href="https://lit.dev/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Lit&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and designed to seamlessly integrate into any web project.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>A Hugo theme component with caniuse shortcode.</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/projects/hugo-fixit/shortcode-caniuse/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:56:32 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/projects/hugo-fixit/shortcode-caniuse/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/github/">GitHub</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="hugo-shortcode-for-caniuse" data-decreased&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hugo shortcode for CanIUse&lt;/span&gt;
